# goflags is DISTINCT from every other documented Go argv parser by
# being a SECURITY-TOOLS-PROVENANCE library used by a coordinated
# suite of penetration-testing tools rather than a general-purpose
# library.  Project Discovery (https://projectdiscovery.io) is a
